## Why This Is Asked
This question tests knowledge of 1D interval stabbing with dynamic updates and top-k queries across overlapping intervals—a common pattern in calendars, ad slot management, and reservation systems.

## Key Concepts
- **Segment tree**: Enables O(log N) node updates for interval operations and point queries
- **Per-node weight multisets**: Maintain counts of overlapping weights using BST/treap for O(log N) rank queries
- **Path aggregation**: Combines structures along the root-to-leaf path to answer sum and kth-largest queries

## Data Layout
1. **Coordinate compression**: Map all interval endpoints to sorted indices (0 to N-1)
2. **Segment tree nodes**: Each node stores a BST of (weight, count) pairs and nodeSum (total weight in that segment)
3. **Query paths**: Both sumWeightsAt and kthLargestWeightAt traverse O(log N) nodes along the path to point x

## Code Example
```javascript
class IntervalSet {
  constructor(points) {
    this.coords = this.compress(points);
    this.tree = this.build(0, this.coords.length - 1);
  }

  compress(points) {
    return [...new Set(points)].sort((a, b) => a - b);
  }

  insertInterval(L, R, w) {
    const l = this.lowerBound(L), r = this.lowerBound(R);
    this.update(this.tree.root, l, r, w, 1);
  }

  eraseInterval(L, R, w) {
    const l = this.lowerBound(L), r = this.lowerBound(R);
    this.update(this.tree.root, l, r, w, -1);
  }

  update(node, L, R, w, delta) {
    if (!node || L > node.r || R < node.l) return;
    if (L <= node.l && node.r <= R) {
      node.bst.insert(w, delta);
      node.sum += w * delta;
      return;
    }
    this.update(node.left, L, R, w, delta);
    this.update(node.right, L, R, w, delta);
  }

  sumWeightsAt(x) {
    const idx = this.lowerBound(x);
    return this.querySum(this.tree.root, idx);
  }

  querySum(node, idx) {
    if (!node) return 0;
    let res = node.sum;
    const mid = Math.floor((node.l + node.r) / 2);
    if (idx <= mid) res += this.querySum(node.left, idx);
    else res += this.querySum(node.right, idx);
    return res;
  }

  kthLargestWeightAt(x, k) {
    const idx = this.lowerBound(x);
    return this.queryKth(this.tree.root, idx, k);
  }

  queryKth(node, idx, k) {
    if (!node) return null;
    const counts = this.getPathCounts(node, idx);
    let lo = 0, hi = this.maxWeight;
    while (lo < hi) {
      const mid = Math.ceil((lo + hi) / 2);
      if (this.countGTE(counts, mid) >= k) lo = mid;
      else hi = mid - 1;
    }
    return lo;
  }
}
```

## Complexity Analysis
- **insertInterval/eraseInterval**: O(log N) nodes × O(log M) BST ops = O(log² N)
- **sumWeightsAt**: O(log N) path traversal
- **kthLargestWeightAt**: O(log N) × O(log maxWeight) = O(log² N)

